    <div style="margin-bottom: 50px;">
        <div><font color="#444444" face="Malgun Gothic"><span style="font-size: 32px; letter-spacing: -2px;">An advance notice to inform</span></font><br><font color="#444444" face="Malgun Gothic"><span style="font-size: 32px; letter-spacing: -2px;"><b>&nbsp;you of the conversion to&nbsp;</b></span></font><br><b style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;; font-size: 32px; letter-spacing: -2px;">dormant member</b><font color="#444444" face="Malgun Gothic"><span style="font-size: 32px; letter-spacing: -2px;">. <img style="margin-top: -40px; margin-right: 10px; float: right;" alt="sleep notice top image" src="/data/mail/img/mailimg_sleep.png"></span></font>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-top: 30px; line-height: 22px;"><font color="#555555" face="Malgun Gothic"><span style="font-size: 13px;">Hello. This is<b> {rc_mallNm}</b>.</span></font><br><font color="#555555" face="Malgun Gothic"><span style="font-size: 13px;">In order to protect the personal information of members who have not accessed the shopping mall for more than {rc_expirationFl} one year, we will convert you to dormant member and securely separate and save the personal information.</span></font><br></div>
    </div>
