        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="height: 43px; padding-right: 20px; padding-left: 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(229, 229, 229); background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243);"><font color="#888888">Separated information</font></td><td style="width: 70%; height: 43px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); padding-left: 20px; font-size: 13px; border-bottom-color: #e5e5e5;; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid;">personal information provided for account signup and/or processing orders</td>
        </tr>
